review_headline: Good for the price. Fits fairly good on 2010 Toyota Camry
review_body: Good for the price!  So far I have put it up in the back window of my 2010 Camry and after several times using my spit and pushing very hard on the suction cups so that you get a black circle effect from looking at it from the outside of the window, they have stuck and have not come off at all.  Make sure you use spit and apply pressure around the entire suction cup to make a secure seal.  Like I said from outside it should look like an all black circle if you have a nice seal going.  Has been up for around one month and has stayed.  It could have been made a little wider as it doesn't cover the entire back window top to bottom, but does seem to be pretty good coverage side to side.
